h_HK/plead-guilty-amendment-one-third-reduction-rule-sentencing/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.onc.hk%2Fzh_HK%2Fplead-guilty-amendment-one-third-reduction-rule-sentencing%2F&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hZqf9GMxMWJW6noFhHuW3mc%3D&h=622a3019\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.onc.hk/zh_HK/plead-guilty-amendment-one-third-reduction-rule-sentencing/</a>"},{"pid":"ffc1051c900e33fea2b06ab433efef4b2be6844e","tid":2186556,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aca579c78805e174cdc044e4c80757cc2c0c0a58","tid":2186556,"uid":121197,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:59:40.000Z","msg":"「你係雙非兒童，有親人關懷，犯案全因社會上言論，令你認為有需要去未經批准遊行表達立場」<br />\n呢句關咩事<br />\n又唔係告佢非法集結/參與未經批准集結"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:04:07.000Z","msg":"姐係父母係香港人果啲，無父母關懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢有冇腦嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7eea35eeb1f36572dd8751243e9a4d435a59a68","tid":2186556,"uid":135274,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d5d2967bdb21dc5c903cf334a0390d31b928298b","tid":2186556,"uid":86980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d8cdd26a5440c2a0146c5dd1451c18002cbcfb30","tid":2186556,"uid":21545,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:56:53.000Z","msg":"程序上都有分早定遲？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:00:36.000Z","msg":"好似話以前無論你在邊一個階段認罪, 都可以獲得1/3減刑<br />\n但係早排改咗例, 在較後階段才認罪, 法官可以酌情減少減刑, 甚至唔減刑<br />\n都係聽返嚟, 有錯請指正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:05:01.000Z","msg":"只要認罪刑會照減，不過個discount由1/3變成20-25%。<br />\n<br />\n今次係fix咗trial date，第一日trial之前認罪，所以話「遲咗少少」係案例上唔係錯誤講法，雖然聽落好撚涼薄。"},{"pid":"53c33ee06d80313b093775f2d7ae125a0b3b1c8d","tid":2186556,"uid":271513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8cdd26a5440c2a0146c5dd1451c18002cbcfb30","tid":2186556,"uid":21545,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:56:53.000Z","msg":"程序上都有分早定遲？"}